**@notice Proposal Codes are used to fire specific code. each number represents a different action*** the following are is a list of prop codes and their actions** 1. Funding Proposal: the address entered is the address receiving funding** 2. Add Member: Allows the community to grant membership to someone who cant afford it** 3. Set Membership Price: Allows the community to set the price of a membership** 4. Set Fee: Allows the community to set the fee taken when using other tokens to purchase/sell DecentraStock
//more options will be added to allow for contract upgrades in the future
